title: Couple With Heart Woman Woman Light Skin Tone Medium Skin Tone
alsoKnownAs: Two Women Holding Hands With Heart
description: Represents a romantic couple composed of two women with different skin tones, symbolizing love and partnership.
apple_vendor_description: This heartwarming representation of a couple on Apple devices features two women with distinct light and medium skin tones, their forms sculpted with Apple's signature glossy 3D shading and smooth gradients. A vibrant red heart, glowing with realistic light, is nestled between them, symbolizing their loving bond with a tender, rounded aesthetic. On Apple devices, this emoji beautifully conveys same-sex love, partnership, and deep affection, fostering inclusive and heartfelt digital communication.
